sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as Llama Stack Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process)
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant IngressCtrl as Ingress Controller<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (HTTPS/443, SA Token)
    Operator->>Operator: Read feature flags from<br/>llama-stack-operator-config ConfigMap
    Operator->>K8sAPI: GET user ConfigMaps, CA bundles<br/>(HTTPS/443, SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ConfigMap data
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests<br/>(Deployment, Service, PVC, NP, PDB, HPA, RB, SA)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered Kubernetes objects
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed resources<br/>(HTTPS/443, SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource created/updated

    Note over Operator,Server: Status Probing

    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/health (HTTP/8321)
    Server-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/providers (HTTP/8321)
    Server-->>Operator: Provider health details
    Operator->>Server: GET /v1/version (HTTP/8321)
    Server-->>Operator: Server version info
    Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH LlamaStackDistribution/status<br/>(HTTPS/443, SA Token)

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: External Client Access (exposeRoute=true)

    Client->>IngressCtrl: HTTP request (80/TCP)
    IngressCtrl->>Server: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>(HTTP/8321)
    Server-->>IngressCtrl: Inference response
    IngressCtrl-->>Client: HTTP response

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 3: Internal Client Access (default)

    Client->>Server: {instance}-service.{ns}.svc.cluster.local<br/>(HTTP/8321, NetworkPolicy enforced)
    Server-->>Client: Inference response
